      "id": "E:note:row514701:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Mr. [**Known lastname 6130**] is a 68 yo with met renal cell CA (to lung and bra",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514701#s1",
      "text": "Mr. [**Known lastname 6130**] is a 68 yo with met renal cell CA (to lung and brain)    admitted on [**2124-2-29**] for week 2 of high dose IL-2 therapy."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514701:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "His last    dose was complicated by shock requiring dopamine and brief atrial   ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514701#s2",
      "text": "His last    dose was complicated by shock requiring dopamine and brief atrial    fibrillation, spontaneously reverting back when dopamine was changed to    neo."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514701:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "His current course was given from [**2-29**] to [**3-4**] and has been    compli",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514701#s3",
      "text": "His current course was given from [**2-29**] to [**3-4**] and has been    complicated by nausea/vomiting, encephalopathy, diarrhea, rigors,    hypotension in the 70s systolic requiring neo ARF with decreasing UOP    (355 total cc's on [**3-5**], none on [**3-4**], + ~ 14L LOC but without detailed    recording of his UOP), and progressive metabolic acidosis despite    bicarb infusion."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514701:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "His Cr has risen progressively from 1.9 on admission    to 6.6 on the evening of",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514701#s4",
      "text": "His Cr has risen progressively from 1.9 on admission    to 6.6 on the evening of transfer."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514701:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Because of his progressive renal    failure, dopamine was added to improve renal",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514701#s5",
      "text": "Because of his progressive renal    failure, dopamine was added to improve renal perfusion."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514701:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt. transferred    here to ICU early morning [**3-6**] for further management of",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514701#s6",
      "text": "Pt. transferred    here to ICU early morning [**3-6**] for further management of hypotension    and renal failure."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514701:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Events;Pt went into rapid Afib with HR 130-150,NBP systolic dropped to    65 ,MD",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514701#s7",
      "text": "Events;Pt went into rapid Afib with HR 130-150,NBP systolic dropped to    65 ,MD [**First Name (Titles) **] [**Last Name (Titles) 1523**],NS 1L bolused,pt already on lovo,added neo and    titrated,HR continued to be as high as 150,cardiverted with 100J,150 J    respectively,ABG done,NBp improved Amiodarone gtt started and team at    [**Last Name (Titles) 1523**],will call wife and update."
    },
